# Activation marker for the observability overlay (ADR-019).
#
# The presence of this `.claude/observability/` directory flips the guarded
# hook self-log ON (see the sibling self-log issue): the shipped-always-dormant
# hooks write to `usage.jsonl` here only when this directory exists. Deleting
# this directory disables the self-log without uninstalling anything.
#
# usage_report.py reads usage.jsonl (when present) for the hooks bucket and
# writes dashboard.html alongside it.
